        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>ics</td>
          <td>positiveInteger</td>
          <td>O</td>
          <td>Indicates which conformance level (1-3) will be used to
					validate the instance document. If not specified, the lowest
					conformance level will be checked (ics=1).</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
